Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely get you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die... Nami... Sanji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Island Where Snow Lives!\NClimb The Drum Rockies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Please look at that!\NWe found them, Wapol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You guys're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do\Nmany rude things to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll chew you guys up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get out of my way.\N--I'll chew you guys up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get out of my way.\N--Humph! You're stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I get out of your way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like what you have on your\Nback and in your arm are half-dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chess! I thought up a new law.\NWrite this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who ignore the king\Nare to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring me already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! First, get the sick and injured ones,\Nwho are ignoring me the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes sir!\N--Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the woman on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Marimo's Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you attack or get struck,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san will feel the whole impact too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. What a coward... It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what a battle in a snowy area is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they've already given up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is a true battle in a snowy area!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The white disguise!\NSnow Powder Makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're so weak,\Nthey'll be dead with just one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check Mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White bears...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lapins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a coincidence.\NLapins never become attached to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do they\Nthink they're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can find the doctor... up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avalanche...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were swallowed by the avalanche...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! U... Usopp-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Come on! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Usopp-san! Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Vivi... Don't wake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just having a beautiful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A field of beautiful flowers out of\Nthis world and a beautiful river... Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're almost in the netherworld!\N--Isn't that Zoro swimming in the river...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wake up! Don't sleep! Wake up!\N--Isn't that Zoro swimming in the river...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 74,000 Usopp Pirates, close in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wake up! Usopp-san,\Ndon't die! Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Usopp-san! Usopp-san!\NUsopp-san! Usopp-san! Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, you saved me, Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about having a\Nnarrow escape from death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--don't you think my face is kinda swollen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I-it's chilblains! Chilblains!\N--don't you think my face is kinda swollen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I-it's chilblains! Chilblains!\N--My head feels kinda heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is why it's not easy\Nto be in a snowy area.\N--My head feels kinda heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is why it's not easy\Nto be in a snowy area.\N--Or should I say my view is kinda narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--More importantly,\N--Or should I say my view is kinda narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--we have to figure out our location\Nand the situation we're in quickly!\N--Or should I say my view is kinda narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--we have to figure out our location\Nand the situation we're in quickly!\N--My lips are kinda big... Kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--we have to figure out our location\Nand the situation we're in quickly!\N--yeah, I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... That was close...\NI saw a field of flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly hitting an avalanche in\Nthis cold... I must've run out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a sort of\Nwinter swimming, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Usopp!\NWhat're you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you lowly bunnies\Nget for going against the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I didn't think I'd use my\Nreal power on mere bunnies, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since they're the most\Nviolent animal in Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait... Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:12:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that... that was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter swimming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After swimming\Nin the river for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea where I was any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was walking while\Ndoing muscle training,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I ended up in a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressed like that?\NYou're stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give me your coat, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san might've gotten sick\Ndue to mental exhaustion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Then your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--One of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--One of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there! There're people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I remember those buildings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! This is Big Horn!\NWe ended up... coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton is already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Dalton-san\Nwould die from an attack like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're Dalton-san's\Nex-subordinates, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're retainers of King Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become Wapol-sama's enemy,\Nyou're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you,\Ndressing like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san's buried under\Nthe snow of the avalanche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We can't dig him out\Nbecause those guys get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any objection,\Ngo right ahead and bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, I remember their clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who attacked\Nus on the sea, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're our enemy, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're our enemy, right?\NWhat's the word? Are they on our side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're our enemy...\Nbut why are you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't so courageous\Nwithout Dalton, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Mr. Bushido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Stop it!\NIf you attack them, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is warm! I'm borrowing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... asked me because of that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look! They're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You!\N--Look! They're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the ship with that\Nguy who blew Wapol-sama away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointing bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good job, Zoro!\NJust as I instructed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Dig everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's all this fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it later! Let's help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! Please be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there. We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine...\NThe antibodies are responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's the cause? Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kestia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Kestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You attend the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Nami-san! I'll cook a\Nnutritious reindeer dish right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the food.\NI just want some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't that reindeer speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I sort of\Nremember him standing on two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue-nosed Reindeer!\NChopper's Secret"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
